songs.title: Silent Night
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Silent night
Holy night
All is calm
All is bright
'Round yon virgin
Mother and child
Holy infant
So tender and mild
Sleep in heavenly peace
Sleep in heavenly peace

[Verse 2]
Silent night
Holy night
Shepards quake
At the sight
Glories stream
From heaven above
Heavenly hosts
Sing Hallelujah
Christ the Savior is born
Christ the Savior is born

[Verse 1]
Silent night
Holy night
All is calm
And all is bright
And 'round yon virgin
Mother and child
Holy infant
So tender and mild
Sleep in heavenly peace
Sleep in heavenly peace
